      <title>Couche-Tard 遭拒后准备确认 Seven & i 的兴趣</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-08/couche-tard-set-to-affirm-seven-i-interest-after-rejection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，Alimentation Couche-Tard Inc. 计划告知 Seven &amp; i Holdings Co.，即使这家日本便利店运营商拒绝了其最初的提议，它仍热衷于进行收购。]]></description>
